snippet.title: PM Narendra Modi Addresses Parivartan Yatra Rally in Kushinagar, UP

localized.description:
Uttar Pradesh Elections 2017: PM Narendra Modi addresses BJP's Parivartan Yatra rally in Kushinagar of Uttar Pradesh. PM Modi speaks over his decision on demonetisation of Rs 500 and RS 1000 notes.
